  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Intimidator Spot 475ZX is a feature-packed powerhouse moving head packs a 250-watt punch for larger events. Intimidator Spot 475ZX comes equipped with a built-in RF receiver for wireless control using the RFC or RFC-XL optional remotes that provide a host of robust remote-control options. An updated CTO color wheel is on board and now software updates are easier than ever with the onboard USB-C port and a new home starting position for the moving head makes programming look smooth and more professional. Dual rotating prisms split the beam for great effects and wider coverage and the motorized zoom is perfect for short or long throw applications. Intimidator Spot 475ZX also boasts powerful gobo projection features including motorized zoom for crisp projections from nearly distance. Set, save, and recall 1 scene manually, directly from the full color LCD display. Beams always remain on the dance floor using the built-in, innovative Totem mode.",
